works.description:
The copyrighted works are webpages that  
have been stolen in their entirety from my website LostWorlds.org and  
reposted at http://moundsandmirsofamexem.blogspot.com

In fact, it appears this blogger site has stolen my entire site and  
reposted it page by page as blog entries on his site. Every post made in  
November 2010 has been stolen from my site.

The other pages on this blogger site appear to be stolen from other  
webpages as well. Nothing on this blogger site is original content and  
should be deleted immediately.
